er. The maser was\nactive on the >10-Jy level only 1990 -- 1992 and 2006/2007. At other times the\nmaser was either absent (<1 Jy) or barely detectable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Feb 2008 16:30:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
